column1: # accession – BioBrick accession number in the iGEM Registry of Standard Biological Parts (https://igem.org/Registry)

# host - E. coli host strain containing the plasmid
# burden.measured – whether the burden of this BioBrick was measured
# sequencing.type - technology used for sequencing this sample
# library.id - identification code for the DNA library that was sequenced (some samples were sequenced multiple times)
